他出生在肯特郡，父母是爱尔兰人，他在那里一直生活到六岁。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-pays-tribute-to-the-greatest-songwriter-of-his-generation-shane-macgowan-after-storied-friendship-3551421">尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave) 向他的密友致敬</a>，称麦高恩是“这一代最伟大的歌曲作家”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-pens-heartfelt-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-and-sinead-oconnor-3552218">随后在</a>麦高恩和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">西妮德·奥康纳</a>去世后写了一篇较长的悼念文章。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">皮特·多尔蒂 (Pete Doherty)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-doherty-hails-bulletproof-shane-macgowan-as-one-of-the-best-lyricists-of-the-last-30-or-40-years-3552035">也表达了同样的观点</a>，认为他是“过去 30 或 40 年”最好的抒情作家之一，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen)</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-calls-shane-macgowan-one-of-my-all-time-favourite-writers-in-touching-tribute-3552221">写了自己的悼词</a>，将麦高恩描述为“我一直以来最喜欢的作家之一”。</p><p>与此同时，U2 也向音乐致敬，他们在拉斯维加斯 Sphere <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-u2-play-a-rainy-night-in-soho-in-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-3552402">翻唱了 The Pogues 的《A Rainy Night in Soho》</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-glen-hansard-friends-cover-the-pogues-a-rainy-night-in-soho-in-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-3553217">格伦·汉萨德还带领一群爱尔兰音乐家</a>演唱了这首歌的一个版本。</p><p>在他去世后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-are-rallying-to-get-the-pogues-fairytale-of-new-york-to-christmas-number-one-after-death-of-shane-macgowan-3551355">歌迷们开始团结起来，力争将波格斯乐队的《纽约童话》打造成圣诞节排行榜第一名</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-pogues-fairytale-of-new-york-re-enters-top-40-following-shane-macgowans-death-3552257">此后它又重新进入了前 40 名</a>。</p><p>肖恩· <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shane-macgowans-cause-of-death-revealed-as-wife-honours-the-blessings-he-brought-3553680">麦高恩 (Shane MacGowan) 的死因揭晓，以纪念妻子“他带来的祝福”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
